data.name: Label7.Text
data.value: The Shopping Cart has some features that you can use when youre here. You can adjust the quantity of your ordered product by clicking on the Code, i.e. R-HUB101, and navigate yourself towards the Options Panel where it says Item Code. Here you can click on the Trash Bin, Decrease, or the Increase buttons to remove the item or adjust its quantity. And on the side, you can see the amount for that product. Now to go back to the Shopping Menu, there is a small utton on the top right hand corner, you can click on this to return to the Ordering Screen. When you want to print your receipt, you can click on the "Receipt-Out" button to proceed to your Receipt. When you're done with your order, you can click on the "Order finished" button. This would ask you if you're done with your order or not before it proceeds to exit itself.

data.name: Label4.Text
data.value: To start on your order, you can direct yourself onto the Category Panel on the side and proceed to click ont he LinkLabels such as the "Axle Hub". When picking items, you can click on the images that you see in front of you and choose the items that you want to get. When you have made a mistake on choosing an item and have already added it on the list, you can simply remove it by clicking on the "Remove Button". When you're done with your selection of the items, you can now click on the "Send to Cart" button to bring it to your Cart. To see what items you have on your Cart, you can click on the Shopping Cart Logo that is on the top right hand of your screen.
